In the early/mid 2000's, I was a 3 Star fan of the then morbidly obese (fatso) Lisa Marie Lampugnale (real name) - Lampanelli, who ran thru  the Comedy Roast circuits before and garnered a modest following. But now her material Smells like Rotten Bacon, that has exceeded it's expiration dates, by a few years! There is nothing new in her latest less fatso transformation, it's become just a meaner Version of the SAME Ethnic humor, racial minority insults, slurs, and stereotypes that are the predominant corpus (no pun intended) of Lampanelli's so called "comedy routines".
Lampanelli is of Italian & Polish descent, how about she focus on some thought-provoking Ethnic humor, racial minority insults, slurs, and stereotypes THERE?
Or, she could add a modern humorous revision as to How the English (UK) refer to the Scott's and the Irish (England's liberal use of theN-word).
Because if you live in America, you have the Freedom to INSULT any Ethnic Group (Cornish, Italians, Jews, Polish, Albanians, Irish, Scot's, German's, Mexicans, French, Greek, etc, etc) or minorities, either in Public or from behind the Safety Glass of your vehicle or Home ... it's called Equal Opportunity, and if this happens to fall on your own family, or ethnicity; well just LOL! There You Go, that's the Spirit! How do you like me Now!
Lisa, is just NOT Funny anymore, so go try Jenny Craig or Weight Watchers for a night cap, maybe you can get new Fat material there.
Yes, I agree that you need to waddle back to the Drawing Board, Lisa, and Look into your own family for new material.
Verdict - New Humor 0 Stars - Weight Loss: 3 Stars.
Lisa Fatpannelli has joined other comedians that rely on feeding from the same Trough of racial insults, slurs and stereotypes. Why? because that's the easiest and laziest choice.
Personally, I don't have a need for that type of bovine scatology, as that is what my family is for! ... Res ipsa Loquitor, People!
